text: イベントコミュ 第1話

trans: Guarantees that a reporter will appear at a random timing no later than three weeks before the end of the final season.

text: 敏腕記者の名刺

trans: Whenever a reporter appears they are guaranteed to be a competent reporter, regardless of the subject you select.

text: 敏腕記者セット
はづきさんへの差し入れ
親愛のお守り
最終シーズンの残り1週までの間に必ず1度「朝コミュ」が起こり、最初に「朝コミュ」か「約束」で親愛度が上昇した時「親愛度急上昇イベント」が必ず発生します
trans: Guarantees a max affection event on the first morning commu or promise. At least 1 morning commu will occur before the end of the final season.
